---
title: Tex Mex Bacon & Veggie Fusilli with Cheddar Cheese & Spring Onion
description: Is it everyone’s favourite time of the week? Yes it is, it’s time for pasta night and we’re pulling out all the stops. Pops of crisp bacon are cooked in a hearty tomato sauce, spiced with our fan-fav Tex-Mex blend and sprinkled over with Cheddar cheese. If you want a bit of fun, garnish with a sprinkle of spring onion.
